ROGUE PLANET THEME ADAPTATION
==============================

This theme adaptation for Rogue Planet includes:
- HTML template (template.html)
- CSS stylesheet with automatic light/dark mode switching (static/style.css)
- Theme documentation (README.md)

The theme adaptation is licensed under the MIT License and is part of the
Rogue Planet project.

